(matrix-*-vector m v)  returns the vector t,
                                   __
                       where t_i = >_j m_(ij) v_j

(matrix-*-matrix m n)  returns the matrix p,
                                      __
                       where p_(ij) = >_k m_(ik) n_(kj)

(transpose m)          returns the matrix n,
